author: Lost in Time
description:
In this video I have colorized and upscaled footage from 1910 to 1920 from London, New York, Norway, China, India, Denmark, Japan and more!

✅ Colorized
✅ Upscaled to 4K
✅ Enhanced using AI
✅ Interpolated to 60 fps
✅ Stabilized (some footage)
